features: Picture Perfect Presents - Use our gold tissue paper for wrapping gifts that are perfect for any occasion. Build anticipation with gold tissue paper sheets. Tissue paper sheets for wrapping gold are a great way to add a touch of luxury to any gift.

Eye-Catching Lustrous Gold - You will receive 40x gold foil sheets (each measuring 50x50cm). Perfect for wrapping presents, crafting, filling gift bags, gift boxes & more. Our gold tissue paper sheets for wrapping are eye-catching & elegant.

Great for Crafting - Not only can you use our gold foil wrapping paper to wrap gifts, you can also use our gold paper to get creative & craft together with your kids. Gold foil paper can be used in a number of ways, as versatile tissue paper gold.

Recyclable – Our gold tissue paper sheets are made from 100% tissue paper and can be placed in the recycling bin after use. Once the excitement is over, simply dispose of the tissue wrapping paper sheets responsibly.

Perfect for Any Occasion – Our 40pk of gift tissue paper sheets will make your friends & family smile by adding a touch of class to gift bags with tissue paper, gift boxes, flowers, hampers, and wrapping tissue paper sheets for any celebration.
